criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Patient undergoing cervical spine surgery;

          -  Male or female;

          -  Aged 18-75 years.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Severe cardiovascular pathology;

          -  Liver disease;

          -  Renal disease;

          -  BMI >35;

          -  Allergies to any anaesthetic drugs.
